2.Pātuhi Pātuhi: Ki te hiahiatia, ka poroa rānei te kī muna (K) kia ōrite ki te rahi paraka o te taumahi hash (ko te tikanga e 512 moka mō SHA-2).
3.Papanga Roto: Ka mahia ngā mahi XOR (tāuke RĀNEI) i runga i te pātuhi padded (K) me ngā uara pūmau e rua e mōhiotia ana ko ngā taimau padding o roto, o waho hoki (ipad me te opad). He tauwhāiti ēnei taimau ki te hātepe hātepe HMAC.
ka whakamahia te ipad ki te XOR me te kī i mua i te hashing.
ka whakamahia te opad ki te XOR me te kī i muri i te hashing.
4.Hash Roto: Kua honoa te padding o roto (ipad XOR K) ki te karere (M), ā, ka hashed tēnei uara paheko mā te whakamahi i te taumahi hash i kōwhiria (H). Mā tēnei ka puta mai he hua hash takawaenga, e tohua ana hei H(ipad XOR K || M).
5.Hash Waho: Kua honoa te padding o waho (opad XOR K) ki te hua hash takawaenga mai i te hipanga tōmua (H(ipad XOR K || M)), ā, ka hashed anō tēnei uara paheko mā te whakamahi i te taumahi hash ōrite (H). Ka puta mai i tēnei mahi hash whakamutunga te HMAC, e whakaaturia ana hei H(opad XOR K || H(ipad XOR K || M)).
Huaputa HMAC: Ko te huaputa o te mahi hash tuarua ko te HMAC, he uara rahi-pūmau ka taea te tāpiri ki te karere hei waihanga i tētahi MAC.  E ai ki runga ake nei " Whakamāramatia mō Hmac"

Heoi anō, kua whakamāramatia kētia e Henström i roto i te kupu whakataki o tēnei kuputuhi kāore i tuhia mō te kaimahi pūkenga, engari "he mea whakarite mō te kaiahuwhenua me ana kaimahi tauhou e tauhou ana ki ngā taipitopito hanga me tō rātou āhua me te kawenga", e whakamārama ana i te kore tauira tātuhi me ngā whakaahuatanga taipitopito ake o ngā tukanga mahi. E hiahia ana ahau kia whakamahia e te AI tēnei hōputu tuhinga:

### **Whakaahuatanga Pātengi Raraunga**
   - **Ūkui Tirohanga Whānui**: Tīmata ki tētahi tirohanga whānui poto o te pātengi raraunga, e miramira ana i tōna whāinga me ngā wae matua pērā ki te HIPANGA 2.
   - **Tīaroaro Tautapa**: Whakahuatia he pēhea te hāngai o ia ripanga me ia āpure ki ngā whakaritenga o te tautapatanga.

### **Ngā Whakaaro me ngā Tāpiritanga**
   - **Ngā Whakaaro Mārama**: Tuhinga i ngā whakaaro i mahia i a koe e hoahoa ana i te pātengi raraunga, pēnei i ngā momo raraunga, te roanga o te āpure, ngā āpure kōwhiringa rānei.
   - **Whakatikatika mō ngā Tāpiritanga**: Whakamāramatia te take i muri i ētahi atu āpure, ripanga rānei i whakaurua e tua atu ana i ngā whakaritenga o te tautapatanga.

### **Ngā Kaupapahere Tauhohenga**
   - **Matapakinga Kaupapahere**: Whakamāramatia ngā kaupapahere tauhohenga e whakamahia ana i roto i te pātengi raraunga, pēnei i te CASCADE i te muku/whakahōu, me te whakamārama he aha i kōwhiria ai.

### **Ngā Whakaahuatanga Ripanga me ngā Momo Raraunga**
   - **Ngā Whakaahuatanga Ripanga Taipitopito**: Mō ia ripanga, homai he whakaahuatanga taipitopito tae atu ki te whāinga, ngā āpure, me ngā momo raraunga.
   - **Pūtake Momo Raraunga**: Whakamāramatia te kōwhiringa o ngā momo raraunga mō ia āpure, e hāngai ana ki te arotahi o te tautapatanga ki ngā momo raraunga tika.

### **Hoahoa Entity-Relationship (ER)**
   - **Hoahoa ER Whānui**: Whakaurua he hoahoa ER taipitopito, e whakaatu ana i ngā pātahitanga i waenga i ngā ripanga me te miramira i ngā kī matua me ngā kī kē.
   - **Tapanga me ngā Poutohu**: Me mātua whakarite he pai te tapanga o te hoahoa ER, ā, kei roto he poutohu mō ngā tohu e whakamahia ana.

### **Tuhinga Hātepe Penapena**
   - **Kōkuhu Hātepe**: Kia mārama te tuhinga i ia hātepe penapena mō te kōkuhu raraunga ki ngā ripanga, e piri ana ki te HIPANGA 3.
   - **Hātepe Uiui**: Tuhinga ia hātepe uiui, me te whakarite kua whakaingoatia kia rite ki te hōputu i whakapūtātia i te HIPANGA 4.
